item.title: [HIVE-22311] Propagate min/max column values from statistics to the optimizer for timestamp type
item.description: Currently stats annotation does not consider timestamp type e.g. for estimates with range predicates.
item.summary: Propagate min/max column values from statistics to the optimizer for timestamp type

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
